    ('ARTH-A 155', 'INTRODUCTION TO AFRICAN ART', '10833', 'Closed', 'MW Monday, Wednesday 8:00 AM–9:15 AM', 'FA 015', 'Barbaro Martinez-Ruiz', 0, NULL, 'Lecture', '3', 'FINE ARTS', ARRAY[]::TEXT[], 'African art in its cultural setting. Major style areas: prehistoric Nok culture, kingdoms of Ife and Benin, Western Sudan, Guinea Coast, equatorial forests, Congo, eastern and southern Africa.', ARRAY['IUB GenEd A&H credit
IUB GenEd World Culture credit
